**Ian Michael Nelson** (born 10 April, 1995)[_[citation
needed](/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed "Wikipedia:Citation needed")_] is an
American actor who portrayed a young Derek Hale in the television series
_[Teen Wolf](/wiki/Teen_Wolf_\(2011_TV_series\) "Teen Wolf \(2011 TV
series\)")_ and Eric Palmer in the drama film _[The
Judge](/wiki/The_Judge_\(2014_film\) "The Judge \(2014 film\)")_.

Nelson is the son of Mark and Janie Nelson. He is a trained singer, dancer,
and actor, and has been featured in the [Macy's Thanksgiving Day
Parade](/wiki/Macy%27s_Thanksgiving_Day_Parade "Macy's Thanksgiving Day
Parade") in New York City. For tenth and eleventh grade, Nelson attended
Forsyth County Day School in [Lewisville, North
Carolina](/wiki/Lewisville,_North_Carolina "Lewisville, North
Carolina").[_[citation needed](/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed
